# Retail Orders - Data Analytics Project

An end-to-end data analytics project where I downloaded a retail orders dataset using Kaggle API, cleaned and processed it with Python (Pandas), loaded it into MySQL, and solved real business problems using SQL.

---

## Business Problems Solved

1. Top 10 highest revenue generating products
2. Top 5 highest selling products in each region
3. Month over month sales growth comparison - 2022 vs 2023
4. For each category, which month had the highest sales
5. Which sub-category had the highest profit growth in 2023 compared to 2022
